{"tid":1743912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：不會特赦村屋僭建","createTime":"2019-11-21T12:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T12:30:18.000Z","uid":186071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"224af0130733c95cab97fe99f4f854a1ab2f5161","tid":1743912,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:23:27.000Z","msg":"政府表示處理新界村屋僭建問題，絕不會有特赦。對於新界村民焚燒發展局局長林鄭月娥的紙紮公仔洩憤，林鄭月娥表示會以平常心看待，若感到人身安全受威脅，會尋求警方介入。<br />\n<br />\n新界村民群起抗議，不滿政府清拆僭建物的做法。政府強調，有危險的村屋僭建物，又或是在今年6月28日或以後，才興建的僭建物，必須取締。<br />\n<br />\n對於鄉議局主席劉皇發揚言以拖字訣，等到新一屆政府上任才繼續商討，林鄭月娥表示，會依法辦事，不可以再拖延下去。<br />\n<br />\n對於村民以焚燒紙紮公仔、棺木，及清拆僭建物的小冊子洩憤，林鄭月娥說，暫時未感到安全受威脅，有需要時會請警方介入。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，當屋宇署人員進入新界清拆僭建物時遇到困難，同樣是找當區的警員協助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=18858&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D18858%26refer%3D&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=014c6afb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D18858%26refer%3D&h=2931ce55\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=18858&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瞓左幾年林鄭捉左幾多個？"},{"pid":"621d9133c475d1601fff4a34be8a2d5d11e85845","tid":1743912,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:24:52.000Z","msg":"對於鄉議局主席劉皇發揚言以拖字訣<br />\n<br />\n最衰都係劉皇發"},{"pid":"a1493ee7d81b19042c59e7f28e12292466b3cff5","tid":1743912,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:25:15.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=394a0c4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=4143273d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=5e8d83d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameAx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=5d48a6dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxRo2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxRo2R.jpg&h=1a7a9910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6b992065a6088356a4d75979b0513db9ecab249","tid":1743912,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:25:18.000Z","msg":"直頭唔檢控 洗鬼特赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7432b4feafda333c19cb65d3067b0dfdcdeecfb","tid":1743912,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdc764f8b0cec369ec056eef6c0ba20492a468c","tid":1743912,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"黑社會係黑警既自己人黎，唔拉得"},{"pid":"0642bba